# Migration data: member-seed-data.json contains member PII (WhatsApp
# numbers, birthdays) and is never committed — regenerate locally with
# GDGWebsite/scripts/regen-seed-json.mjs when needed. team-members.json is
# the public roster (same data the website already displays) and IS tracked
# so the importer works from a fresh clone.
scripts/data/*
!scripts/data/team-members.json
